# Generator script (for posterity, in case we need to
# recreate or modify).
N=255
function cophdr() {
    local F=$1
    cat > $F <<EOF
// Copyright 2025 The Go Authors. All rights reserved.
// Use of this source code is governed by a BSD-style
// license that can be found in the LICENSE file.
EOF
}
#
# Go source
#
cophdr a.go
echo "package main" >> a.go
echo "func main() { " >> a.go
I=0
while [ $I -lt $N ]; do
    echo "  t${I}()" >> a.go
    I=`expr $I + 1`
done
echo "}" >> a.go
go
echo  >> a.go
I=0
while [ $I -lt $N ]; do
    echo "func t${I}() " >> a.go
    I=`expr $I + 1`
done
#SALT=`date '+%Y%M%d%h%m%s'`
#echo "var foofoo = \"${SALT}\"" >> a.go
gofmt -w a.go
#
# Assembly sources
#
cophdr a.s
I=0
while [ $I -lt $N ]; do
    echo "TEXT ·t${I}(SB),0,\$0" >> a.s
    echo "	RET" >> a.s
    echo >> a.s
    I=`expr $I + 1`
done
